===Etymology===
From {{uder|en|de|Xylem}}, from {{uder|en|grc|ξύλον||wood}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|zīʹləm}}, {{IPA|en|/ˈzaɪ.ləm/}}
* {{rhymes|en|aɪləm|s=2}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{lb|en|botany}} A [[vascular]] [[tissue]] in land plants primarily responsible for the distribution of water and minerals taken up by the roots; also the primary component of [[wood]].
